{"service_name": "Content strategy", "service_id": "7773868817462335", "company_name": "Scroll LLP", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Scroll LLP\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Content strategy\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Scroll provides content strategy services that follow industry best practices. The content strategists can implement strategies that determine the management of content throughout the entire content lifecycle to advance the organisational objectives through the optimisation of content. This may include optimising content for multichannel publishing or omnichannel delivery.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Prototyping and implementation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Implementing systems for inbound marketing, content marketing, across communication strategies\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Defining requirements and creating deliverables across the entire content lifecycle\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Analysing results of content inventories, quantitative audits, and qualitative analyses\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Scoping the overall content requirements and potential content sources\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Migrate legacy content and ensure it meets content engineering standards\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Create or oversee taxonomies and metadata frameworks\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Write new content, semantically structure and tag it\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensure that content conforms to Search Engine Optimization best practices\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Develop content matrices and map content during site redesigns\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Scroll\u2019s Chief Information Officer has helped define industry best practices\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensures that content meets the needs of multiple user groups\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Makes content adaptive for multichannel publishing and omnichannel application\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Optimises content for use with responsive designs\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Umbrella strategy that coordinates use of various sorts of content\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Unified strategy across guidance, social, marketing, and technical content\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Content is optimised for delivery and meets accessibility requirements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Creates content lifecycles to manage content efficiently over multiple iterations\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Content strategies based on organisational objectives and user needs\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Innovative solutions for content presentation, content management, workflow, and maintenance\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3450 to \u00a3775 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Including VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Education pricing available\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Termination costs apply\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92710/7773868817462335-pricing-document-2015-10-06-1206.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n     